channel.title: Diaries of a Woodcutter
channel.description:
Basically I am trying to go for 99 Woodcut and 99 Fletching. This is my story.
[center][size=14pt]Day 1[/size][/center] [hr] Today I got 67 Fletching and 93 Woodcutting and decided to start this diary/journal or whatever you want to call it. I have a lot to go so I decided to go for fletching first.
[center][size=14pt]Day 2[/size][/center] [hr] Today I bought 4320 Willow Logs and hope to get 70 fletching. From there I'm going to fletch 16,807 Yew Logs and String them to 85 fletching, then fletch and string 53,324 mage longs to 99!
